text: False Identity (French: Fausse identité) is a 1947 French crime movie directed by André Chotin. It stars Louise Carletti, Georges Rollin, Raymond Bussières, Frank Villard, Simone Deguyse, Marie Bizet and Renée Devillers. ==Other websites== * Category:1947 crime movies Category:French crime movies Category:Movies directed by André Chotin
title: False Identity (1947 movie)
